---
title: Mustard & Apricot-Glazed John Dory with Roast Veggie Toss & Garlic Aioli
description: Fruity sauces are amazing when they are coated over a fresh white fish. The best of them all is this apricot sauce! We wonder what would happen if it was added to a mustard glaze? There’s only one way to find out!
